{"tid":2012335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【慣犯現形 揭PK鄧9年僭建史】","createTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T14:37:14.000Z","uid":4562,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c694f923eece1e4f1215115a42af440948ee4370","tid":2012335,"uid":4562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/95780826_2962544683811436_8271430576221716480_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=eH2Xls3HLmoAX-qKGal&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=1d38d1dfc48a2b75fb6cae4f92efbbf7&amp;oe=5EE02F0B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F95780826_2962544683811436_8271430576221716480_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DeH2Xls3HLmoAX-qKGal%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D1d38d1dfc48a2b75fb6cae4f92efbbf7%26oe%3D5EE02F0B&h=de909190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【慣犯現形 揭PK鄧9年僭建史】<br />\n<br />\n警務處長鄧炳強5月5日﹝上星期二﹞到立法會保安事務委員會解釋九龍塘寶能閣租住單位天台僭建事件。他在會上表示：「第一，我係一個比較敏感的人物，下次去搵屋係咪應該搵個專業人士望清楚睇清楚係咪有不合法建設；第二，事實上，今次我係長左時間先搬走，事後睇番係咪應該早啲搬呢，以免惹來好多猜疑。」<br />\n<br />\nPK這番話，自然是想公眾相信他是無心之失﹝責任全歸地產經紀﹞，但我們經調查發現，PK在遷入寶能閣之前，起碼兩度持有存在明顯違規僭建物的物業，根本就是「僭建慣犯」。<br />\n<br />\n根據土地註冊處及消息人士資料，PK自2002年起先後擁有四個物業，兩個是多層住宅單位，兩個是低密度住宅，後兩者包括2002年8月至2004年7月持有的西貢柏麗灣別墅17號屋，以及2012年5月至2016年5月持有的元朗錦綉花園M段第二街第8號屋。<br />\n<br />\n2003年11月25日由測繪處拍攝的航空照片﹝編號CW52902﹞顯示，柏麗灣別墅17號的天台有兩處加了上蓋，地下後花園亦有一構築物，兩者均不包括在柏麗灣別墅的核准建築物圖則中，屬違例僭建。<br />\n<br />\n2015年9月24日拍攝，編號CS61023的測繪處航空照片則拍到PK錦綉花園住所的後花園白色構築物。根據錦綉花園的核准建築物圖則及屋苑公契，後花園的構築物屬僭建。由於2012年1月的航拍照仍未見到該構築物，該構築物有可能是在PK持有單位期間僭建的。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，PK由錦綉花園遷入租用的九龍塘寶能閣高層連天台僭建單位，即是由一個有僭建物的物業遷到另一個有更大型僭建物的物業。<br />\n<br />\n「如果我有違法行為，有責任的話，係絕對唔會逃避。」事實是，PK在西貢和元朗錦綉花園已經逃避了至少兩次，更涉嫌將有僭建的物業轉手他人。明天PK去元朗區議會接受質詢，就請他慢慢向議員們解釋。<br />\n<br />\n#做每件事都有代價<br />\n#犯法就是犯法一定要負責<br />\n#天網恢恢疏而不漏<br />\n#提醒身邊人<br />\n<br />\nfrom 八鄉朱凱廸 Chu Hoi Dick facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/photos/a.203826656349933/2962544677144770/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchuhoidick%2Fphotos%2Fa.203826656349933%2F2962544677144770%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=f3902edf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/photos/a.203826656349933/2962544677144770/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"852620b0909b8bc6655889c0403e5e42d760478e","tid":2012335,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"509f1ef8afd601b2f2b7e393891bff15d6dbbd9b","tid":2012335,"uid":320192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:25:25.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律 老屈<br />\n就係要依啲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c9d45803e5bacc7fc6d796d622cf35dc7c8744f","tid":2012335,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要行刑式打記者啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a12c0716f4e9be9fda7cbb6a6fb86b1feed7231","tid":2012335,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"聽日佢入元朗國"},{"pid":"7f467a42267e4c26cba71842f02c98e0535ed964","tid":2012335,"uid":320192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律 老屈<br />\n推推推！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251483e5268a35b1e37f82c3d76780eb4a29e87c","tid":2012335,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"PK : 免費加大實用面積！成龍教落:「有食唔食，罪大惡極，食完最緊要唔認數就得。」"},{"pid":"d8e249fa109f02d5ce1b2adf89f00049b093331d","tid":2012335,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:27:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35db4242d6b95e2008e93a7c3f52c837c634b56","tid":2012335,"uid":125670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41dab68b8907478c85383f9a021392b78be02c9","tid":2012335,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8zvoZz0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8zvoZz0.png&h=762ab6bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本土研究社 Liber Research Community<br />\n<br />\n【輔警一哥僭建霸地企圖私了】<br />\n<br />\n今日輔警一哥楊祖賜俾《明報》同我地揭發佢知法犯法，僭建霸地9年佔車房。佢最新回應呢個話唔算係「固定建築物」，隨時可以拆得，所以唔算係僭建。警方發言人就話佢已經搵左測量師睇，唔駛做野。<br />\n<br />\n你話佢呢個唔係「固定建築物」，阿一哥，不如你試下移動個構建物黎睇下? <br />\n<br />\n如果話用可拆板起個建築就唔計僭建，咁不如試下喺你間丁屋起成座IFC做太陽能發電?<br />\n<br />\n圍封左就係僭建，僭建就係違法，屋宇署規則寫得清清楚楚 (參考屋宇署：新界豁免管制屋宇的小型環保及適意設施)，你做地產根本自己最清楚，企圖混淆視聽，大家一齊睇相判斷。<br />\n<br />\n以為自己做地產又做警察，在西貢北港新村迴旋處最當眼個間丁屋起僭建物，一樓裝個CCTV監控，就冇人夠膽揭發你? 實在太天真了。<br />\n<br />\n提提大家，呢位花名叫新地槍王既輔警一哥楊祖賜，在雨傘到反修例都有積極參與行動，上年十二月重被續約。根據輔警通訊，佢任內最自豪既政積係發展左個輔警情報網，鼓勵輔警平日寫報告「篤灰」，搞到啲輔警冇哂朋友。<br />\n<br />\n剃人頭者人亦剃之，今日鼓勵人「篤灰」者終被「篤灰」。<br />\n<br />\n犯法就係犯法，邊個批准話你自己搵測量師私了年事? 地政屋宇署點解唔立即做野，係咪因為佢係輔警一哥又係地產商，所以又唔見人?<br />\n<br />\n請幫手廣傳開去，唔好俾呢位輔警一哥語言偽術蒙混過關。<br />\n<br />\n#祖賜移動城堡<br />\n#香港警察知法犯法<br />\n#輔警一哥楊祖賜<br />\n#篤人灰者人亦篤之<br />\n#土地研究<br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n圖片來源：明報<br />\n<br />\n明報頭版：輔警一哥涉天台僭建霸官地　屋署地署調查<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2yOaDS3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yOaDS3&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=2a55c3f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2yOaDS3</a><br />\n<br />\n屋宇署：可裝設在現存和新建新界豁免管制屋宇的小型環保及適意設施 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YPHQaa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YPHQaa&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=0ae9f228\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YPHQaa</a><br />\n<br />\n--<br />\n👓 官商鄉黑警和你check　月捐支持土地研究<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=673ee4d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=5f15767f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/localresearch/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"}]}